**story**

once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey, who decided on a berry tree.
which walls on the bank of a river. In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife.
one day, the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree. 
the kind hearted monkey decided to give him fruits
the crocodile came back for the next two days for more fruits as he loved them
as days passed by the crocodile and monkey became best friends